verbose_text: As for the tumor size, the miR-222 levels in tumors with a maximum diameter of> = 5 cm (3.13 +/-0.66) was significantly higher compared with that in tumors of < 5 cm in maximum diameter (2.37 +/-0.85; P = 0.02); while significantly lower BBC3 levels were identified in tumors sized maximum> = 5 cm (2.29 +/-0.36) than in those of < 5 cm in maximum size (2.88 +/-0.44; P = 0.04).
